1
00:00:18,290 --> 00:00:20,770
Beware of fire and thieves.

2
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:25,380
Stay alert for fire.

3
00:00:43,680 --> 00:00:45,079
(Delivery Room)

4
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:48,000
(Surgery in Progress)

5
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,519
(Wu Shichuan, Director of Health Bureau)

6
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:01,480
(Zhao Wan'er, Wife of Wu Shichuan)

7
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:10,240
(Keep Quiet, No Noise)

8
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:24,120
(Keep Quiet, No Noise)

9
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:32,459
I summon the Gu shaman.

10
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:35,209
Big spirits, small spirits, Toad Spirit,

11
00:01:35,210 --> 00:01:37,730
come and claim his life.

12
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:42,620
I, Gu Xishan,

13
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:44,409
died with a grievance because of you.

14
00:01:44,410 --> 00:01:46,290
My soul has never found peace.

15
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:49,579
Today, I borrow this body
to place this curse upon you.

16
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:53,220
One day, you will end up just like this.

17
00:01:53,580 --> 00:01:55,500
Your body will swell until you die.

18
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:58,090
Your body will swell until you die!

19
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:41,220
A ghost!

20
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:42,970
A ghost!

21
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:54,919
(St. Anton Hospital)

22
00:02:54,920 --> 00:03:00,640
=Cases Between Us=

23
00:03:02,370 --> 00:03:05,329
=Episode 1=
We've reached the final lot

24
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:07,370
of today's auction.

25
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:11,340
Now, let's invite
the appraisers to examine it.

26
00:03:15,490 --> 00:03:18,016
Shape and structure,
inscription, material,

27
00:03:18,016 --> 00:03:20,010
and craftsmanship, all check out.

28
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:22,416
A true masterpiece.

29
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,340
(Master Song, Antiques Dealer)
Master Tian,

30
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:26,329
do take a good look.

31
00:03:26,330 --> 00:03:27,369
Don't worry.

32
00:03:27,370 --> 00:03:28,500
I've seen enough.

33
00:03:30,650 --> 00:03:32,580
Such a delicate Huamei bird,
but you've ruined it.

34
00:03:32,704 --> 00:03:35,540
A fine Huamei should have three shades
of blue and four shades of yellow.

35
00:03:35,552 --> 00:03:36,970
You have to take it out every day.

36
00:03:36,980 --> 00:03:38,340
It has good features.

37
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:39,609
Feed it

38
00:03:39,610 --> 00:03:40,970
three live crickets.

39
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:43,019
Mix in mung bean flour

40
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:43,649
and egg yolk.

41
00:03:43,650 --> 00:03:45,489
It soothes the throat
and eases heatiness.

42
00:03:45,490 --> 00:03:46,529
Thank you, everyone.

43
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:47,740
You have to feed it.

44
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:52,020
Master Song.

45
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:59,280
(Zhao Shaoshang)

46
00:04:01,210 --> 00:04:02,300
Young Master Zhao,

47
00:04:03,420 --> 00:04:05,220
long time no see.

48
00:04:05,490 --> 00:04:06,650
Good day.

49
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:09,810
I heard you've acquired a treasure.

50
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:13,410
Word travels fast, huh?

51
00:04:13,484 --> 00:04:14,650
Mind if I have a look?

52
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:16,610
Maybe not.

53
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:21,490
But according to Master Tian
from Liulichang Antique Market,

54
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:23,380
it's a masterpiece.

55
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:26,730
Master Tian must be over eighty.

56
00:04:26,770 --> 00:04:28,900
Are you sure
his eyesight is still that good?

57
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:32,730
When Master Tian served in the palace,

58
00:04:32,820 --> 00:04:33,900
you hadn't even

59
00:04:34,290 --> 00:04:35,530
been weaned yet.

60
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,530
Master Song,

61
00:04:39,788 --> 00:04:41,515
when my grandfather
was the Superintendent

62
00:04:41,516 --> 00:04:43,052
of the Imperial Household,

63
00:04:43,290 --> 00:04:43,969
Tian Youfu

64
00:04:43,970 --> 00:04:46,508
used to clean chamber pots
at the Penal Servants' Quarter.

65
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:48,610
You really don't mind the smell?

66
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:51,547
We're done here.

67
00:04:51,548 --> 00:04:52,650
Please excuse me.

68
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:55,970
So you only look at the outside,
not the inside?

69
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:57,459
Dip a probe in seal paste

70
00:04:57,460 --> 00:04:59,410
and examine the bottom.

71
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:03,900
Master Song, go ahead.

72
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:05,530
There's nothing to worry about.

73
00:05:05,650 --> 00:05:07,379
A genuine piece has nothing to hide.

74
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:08,139
Please.

75
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:09,210
Examine it again.

76
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:11,729
At least put
Young Master Zhao's mind at ease

77
00:05:11,730 --> 00:05:13,499
and satisfy our curiosity.

78
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:14,049
Right?

79
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:14,779
Exactly.

80
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:15,700
That's right.

81
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:16,970
Alright.

82
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:18,700
In that case,

83
00:05:19,210 --> 00:05:20,650
I'll satisfy your curiosity.

84
00:05:37,210 --> 00:05:39,340
Made by Zhao Shaoshang...

85
00:05:40,410 --> 00:05:43,490
A replica?

86
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:46,410
Zhao,

87
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:48,490
you set me up!

88
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:50,580
I told you before.

89
00:05:50,900 --> 00:05:51,769
Antiques,

90
00:05:51,770 --> 00:05:54,636
especially our national treasures,
are not to be sold to Westerners.

91
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:56,970
Sell cheap junk if you want.

92
00:05:57,404 --> 00:05:58,340
But if you dare sell

93
00:05:58,380 --> 00:05:59,619
even one national treasure,

94
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:01,340
I have means and ways to deal with you.

95
00:06:01,530 --> 00:06:02,379
However much you made

96
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:03,460
from those foreigners,

97
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:04,850
I'll make sure

98
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:07,290
you lose twice as much.

99
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:10,409
Zhao,

100
00:06:10,410 --> 00:06:13,610
you've ruined my business
over and over again.

101
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:15,729
If I don't teach you a lesson today,

102
00:06:15,730 --> 00:06:18,459
you'll think I'm all talk!

103
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:19,019
Bring it on!

104
00:06:19,020 --> 00:06:19,939
Beat him to death!

105
00:06:19,940 --> 00:06:20,849
Traitor Song,

106
00:06:20,850 --> 00:06:22,170
you dare touch me?

107
00:06:22,210 --> 00:06:24,410
- Have you lost your mind?
- Don't run. Stop.

108
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:26,050
Stop right there!

109
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:45,320
(Yuan Hong)

110
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:47,970
Stop!

111
00:06:51,850 --> 00:06:52,700
Nice!

112
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:04,289
This is the capital.

113
00:07:04,290 --> 00:07:05,459
It's broad daylight now.

114
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:06,731
Do you know what the penalty is

115
00:07:06,732 --> 00:07:08,220
for beating someone in a group?

116
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:09,900
Mister...

117
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:11,140
It's him.

118
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:12,769
He set me up!

119
00:07:12,770 --> 00:07:13,850
So what if I did?

120
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:16,409
I did it on purpose. I'll make you
lose even more next time.

121
00:07:16,410 --> 00:07:18,050
Did you hear that?

122
00:07:18,896 --> 00:07:21,390
Do you know who my father is?
Do you know who you're messing with?

123
00:07:21,650 --> 00:07:23,650
Next time, I'll bankrupt you.
Mark my words!

124
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:27,289
Don't leave.

125
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:28,700
Don't leave me behind.

126
00:07:29,090 --> 00:07:30,530
What's that got to do with me?

127
00:07:35,650 --> 00:07:36,769
Why are you following me?

128
00:07:36,770 --> 00:07:38,499
Who's following you?
This isn't your road.

129
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:39,730
I'll walk wherever I want.

130
00:07:41,650 --> 00:07:42,650
You...

131
00:07:46,650 --> 00:07:47,649
Brat.

132
00:07:47,650 --> 00:07:48,529
Get him!

133
00:07:48,530 --> 00:07:49,529
Stop!

134
00:07:49,530 --> 00:07:50,289
Stop!

135
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:51,290
Stop!

136
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:52,610
Stop!

137
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:56,970
Bite them.

138
00:07:57,140 --> 00:07:58,849
I didn't raise you for nothing.

139
00:07:58,850 --> 00:08:00,530
Bite those traitors!

140
00:08:01,850 --> 00:08:03,140
Good boy, Dabao.

141
00:08:04,530 --> 00:08:05,320
Young Master,

142
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:07,120
(Zhao Cai)
Master wants you home immediately.

143
00:08:07,136 --> 00:08:08,380
Something had happened.

144
00:08:20,850 --> 00:08:23,459
Young Master, no matter what happens,
you mustn't talk back.

145
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:24,819
Master and Madam

146
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:26,090
both look furious.

147
00:08:27,904 --> 00:08:29,780
I think I'll stay out of sight
for a few days.

148
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:31,649
You might dodge it today,
but not tomorrow.

149
00:08:31,650 --> 00:08:33,370
At worst, you'll just take a beating.

150
00:08:33,380 --> 00:08:34,099
Don't worry.

151
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:36,256
I've got some imported
wound ointment ready for you.

152
00:08:36,620 --> 00:08:38,180
You're not the one getting beaten.

153
00:08:41,884 --> 00:08:43,996
If I don't divorce him,
he'll bring me down with him.

154
00:08:44,170 --> 00:08:45,769
Calm down, Wan'er.

155
00:08:45,770 --> 00:08:46,569
It's not that bad.

156
00:08:46,570 --> 00:08:48,219
How am I supposed to calm down?

157
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:50,928
Ever since it happened, the front gate's
been swarming with reporters.

158
00:08:50,930 --> 00:08:53,520
They're waiting with cameras
to watch us make fools of ourselves.

159
00:08:53,530 --> 00:08:55,569
I've never been
so humiliated in my life.

160
00:08:55,570 --> 00:08:57,839
(Tong Mengling)

161
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:00,289
(Zhao Chengru)

162
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:01,099
Mother.

163
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:02,169
Wan'er.

164
00:09:02,170 --> 00:09:03,099
My Wan'er.

165
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:03,890
Mother.

166
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:06,979
There, there, Wan'er.

167
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:08,169
I'm here.

168
00:09:08,170 --> 00:09:09,770
If you're unhappy, come home.

169
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:12,130
Don't! Don't!

170
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:14,340
Look at all these treasures
on the floor.

171
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:15,809
What's going on?

172
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:17,371
Getting divorced again?

173
00:09:17,372 --> 00:09:19,308
Shichuan is taking another concubine?

174
00:09:20,810 --> 00:09:22,304
Yixing clay teapot from the Wanli era!

175
00:09:22,336 --> 00:09:24,010
Don't throw it!

176
00:09:24,020 --> 00:09:25,580
What's going on?

177
00:09:25,810 --> 00:09:27,970
(Morning News)
Don't you read papers?

178
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:31,200
Concubine of Director Wu Shichuan
of Health Bureau

179
00:09:31,216 --> 00:09:33,024
of Internal Affairs Department
was possessed

180
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,250
and died with the baby.

181
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:36,060
What happened?

182
00:09:36,100 --> 00:09:36,809
The concubine died

183
00:09:36,810 --> 00:09:38,409
in the delivery room.

184
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:39,979
Shichuan was scared out of his wits.

185
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:41,409
He came home burning with fever

186
00:09:41,410 --> 00:09:42,730
and babbling nonsense.

187
00:09:43,650 --> 00:09:44,379
Go away!

188
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:46,019
What are you trying to do, Gu Xishan?

189
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:47,540
Ghost!

190
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:48,899
Don't come near!

191
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:50,700
Get out!

192
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,060
Don't come near me!

193
00:09:52,770 --> 00:09:53,379
Gu Xishan,

194
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,730
don't you try to kill me.

195
00:09:55,170 --> 00:09:56,587
Is he possessed?

196
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,490
You'd better get a master
to take a look at him.

197
00:09:58,512 --> 00:09:59,490
We already did.

198
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:01,019
His mother spent a fortune

199
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:03,420
to invite a Taoist master.

200
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:05,409
Form the array.

201
00:10:05,410 --> 00:10:06,180
Freeze!

202
00:10:11,290 --> 00:10:12,340
Evil spirit!

203
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:18,010
Heavenly gods and earthly spirits.

204
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:20,770
By divine command, be done at once!

205
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,300
Break!

206
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,049
(Wu Shichuan)

207
00:10:38,050 --> 00:10:39,340
Toad Gu poison?

208
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:42,289
It's extremely vicious.
Once you're poisoned,

209
00:10:42,290 --> 00:10:44,169
your belly swells like you're pregnant,

210
00:10:44,170 --> 00:10:47,250
and eventually swells to death.

211
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:48,449
Shichuan

212
00:10:48,450 --> 00:10:49,540
is in huge trouble.

213
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:52,139
Where did you hear that nonsense?

214
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:54,409
The medicine worked.
He's clear-headed now.

215
00:10:54,410 --> 00:10:55,169
If he's fine,

216
00:10:55,170 --> 00:10:56,610
why are you getting divorced?

217
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,070
Smash your own thing.

218
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:00,250
Why are you smashing mine?
I didn't do anything to you.

219
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:01,739
His family says Wu Shichuan's sick

220
00:11:01,740 --> 00:11:03,040
because I bring bad luck to him.

221
00:11:03,050 --> 00:11:03,850
How is this my fault?

222
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:04,929
What's it to me?

223
00:11:04,930 --> 00:11:06,289
I asked him

224
00:11:06,290 --> 00:11:07,099
about Gu Xishan.

225
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:07,739
That jerk told me

226
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:08,979
to mind my own business.

227
00:11:08,980 --> 00:11:10,030
As if I'd put up with that.

228
00:11:10,048 --> 00:11:11,220
We got into a huge fight,

229
00:11:11,410 --> 00:11:14,090
and he slapped me.

230
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:14,979
Mother.

231
00:11:14,980 --> 00:11:15,899
He hit you?

232
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,219
You must divorce him!

233
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:18,610
He hit you?

234
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:20,300
I don't believe it.

235
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:22,169
Don't.

236
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:23,730
Enough. Stop arguing.

237
00:11:27,050 --> 00:11:28,820
Isn't Shichuan getting better?

238
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,384
As long as he's alright.

239
00:11:30,432 --> 00:11:31,040
Father,

240
00:11:31,050 --> 00:11:32,449
what about my reputation?

241
00:11:32,450 --> 00:11:34,370
The truth will speak for itself.

242
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:36,180
Once this blows over, you'll be alright.

243
00:11:36,450 --> 00:11:38,379
You always say

244
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:39,449
the same thing.

245
00:11:39,450 --> 00:11:40,649
But nothing ever changes.

246
00:11:40,650 --> 00:11:41,940
What are you getting at?

247
00:11:41,990 --> 00:11:43,451
Alright. Wan'er will stay here for now.

248
00:11:43,460 --> 00:11:45,150
Once things settle down
at the Wu family,

249
00:11:45,168 --> 00:11:46,640
we'll decide what to do next.

250
00:11:46,650 --> 00:11:48,370
Absolutely not!

251
00:11:48,930 --> 00:11:50,569
Yes. Absolutely yes!

252
00:11:50,570 --> 00:11:51,049
Wan'er,

253
00:11:51,050 --> 00:11:51,859
I'll look into it.

254
00:11:51,860 --> 00:11:53,300
I'll clear your name.

255
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:55,649
Are you back to stir up trouble?

256
00:11:55,650 --> 00:11:56,689
You spend all day

257
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:57,809
doing nothing useful.

258
00:11:57,810 --> 00:11:59,259
What exactly can you investigate?

259
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:00,300
Father,

260
00:12:00,980 --> 00:12:02,569
they've always blamed Wan'er for not

261
00:12:02,570 --> 00:12:04,510
having a child.
That's why they took a concubine.

262
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:05,424
Now something happened

263
00:12:05,456 --> 00:12:07,300
to the concubine,
and they're blaming her again.

264
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:08,971
Insulting her
is insulting the Zhao family.

265
00:12:08,972 --> 00:12:10,809
How are we supposed to face people?

266
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:11,619
Good.

267
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:13,169
Then don't go out.

268
00:12:13,170 --> 00:12:14,929
Come. Take the young master
back to his room.

269
00:12:14,930 --> 00:12:15,769
Other than meals,

270
00:12:15,770 --> 00:12:17,210
he's not allowed to come downstairs.

271
00:12:18,690 --> 00:12:20,289
Father, don't do this.

272
00:12:20,290 --> 00:12:21,610
Father.

273
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:23,700
Stop kidding. Let go.

274
00:12:24,290 --> 00:12:25,340
Let go of me.

275
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:26,730
Get off of me.

276
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:28,379
You're locking me up?

277
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:29,649
Seriously?

278
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:30,409
Open the door!

279
00:12:30,410 --> 00:12:31,580
Open!

280
00:12:32,170 --> 00:12:33,649
I remember what you two look like.

281
00:12:33,650 --> 00:12:34,460
Fine.

282
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:36,610
You'd better hope
I never see you again!

283
00:12:58,930 --> 00:13:00,220
What are you doing here?

284
00:13:01,770 --> 00:13:03,610
I'm taking your room from now on.

285
00:13:04,450 --> 00:13:05,610
What do you mean?

286
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,360
My room doesn't get
much of a cross breeze.

287
00:13:07,376 --> 00:13:08,730
It's too hot to sleep at night.

288
00:13:09,050 --> 00:13:09,940
I see.

289
00:13:10,570 --> 00:13:11,820
I don't mind the heat.

290
00:13:12,620 --> 00:13:14,739
I heard you just got
an ivory bamboo mat.

291
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:15,619
And also

292
00:13:15,620 --> 00:13:17,049
that Italian electric fan.

293
00:13:17,050 --> 00:13:19,460
You're asking for too much.

294
00:13:23,620 --> 00:13:24,610
Fine.

295
00:13:24,810 --> 00:13:26,250
I'll bring them to you right now.

296
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:30,130
Young Master, are you really
going to look into this?

297
00:13:30,140 --> 00:13:31,219
What choice do I have?

298
00:13:31,220 --> 00:13:32,656
Didn't you see how determined she was?

299
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:34,590
If I don't find the truth,
she'll never leave here.

300
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,590
If she doesn't leave,
I'll never have a day's peace!

301
00:13:36,608 --> 00:13:37,440
Is it really that bad?

302
00:13:37,450 --> 00:13:38,811
Young Lady treats you pretty well.

303
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:40,640
When outsiders pick on me,
she stands up for me.

304
00:13:40,650 --> 00:13:43,290
But if not, she beats me up. I've
spent years collecting my treasures.

305
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:44,539
How many will survive her temper?

306
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:46,652
She even tore up Wu Daozi's painting.
(*A Tang Dynasty painter)

307
00:13:47,530 --> 00:13:48,370
No.

308
00:13:48,570 --> 00:13:49,890
I've got to get her out of here.

309
00:13:49,930 --> 00:13:51,060
First, we need to find out

310
00:13:51,140 --> 00:13:52,610
who Gu Xishan was.

311
00:13:52,690 --> 00:13:53,707
Gu Xishan?

312
00:13:53,710 --> 00:13:56,304
Shichuan was poisoned, and they say
it's the work of an evil spirit.

313
00:13:56,310 --> 00:13:57,680
That means they've had beef before.

314
00:13:57,728 --> 00:13:59,060
Where are we going now?

315
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:00,700
If he died with a grievance,

316
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:02,580
there has to be a household record.

317
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:04,700
We're going to the police department.

318
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:12,000
(Jingshi Police Department)

319
00:14:27,380 --> 00:14:29,220
Everyone, the meat's here.

320
00:14:29,340 --> 00:14:29,979
Where were you?

321
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:30,899
What took you so long?

322
00:14:30,900 --> 00:14:32,370
Hurry. Throw the meat in.

323
00:14:34,930 --> 00:14:35,770
Fatty.

324
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:40,490
I've got better aim.

325
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:49,120
(Strong Nation)

326
00:14:50,050 --> 00:14:50,809
Stop playing.

327
00:14:50,810 --> 00:14:51,739
Stop eating.

328
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:52,890
Clean everything up.

329
00:14:53,410 --> 00:14:54,820
Hurry up!

330
00:14:54,848 --> 00:14:55,640
Clean the place up.

331
00:14:55,650 --> 00:14:56,660
Is everything ready?

332
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:59,040
Is he the new chief of Division Four
who came in yesterday?

333
00:14:59,050 --> 00:14:59,859
Yeah.

334
00:14:59,860 --> 00:15:01,690
(Division Four Chief's Office)
He's a big deal.

335
00:15:01,712 --> 00:15:03,890
He was parachuted in.
Division Four was created for him.

336
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:05,019
Not necessarily.

337
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:07,409
Division Four is full
of the department's leftovers.

338
00:15:07,410 --> 00:15:09,820
Whether it's a promotion or a demotion
is anyone's guess.

339
00:15:10,112 --> 00:15:11,970
- Good day, Chief Yuan.
- Good day, Chief Yuan.

340
00:15:17,810 --> 00:15:18,569
Yang?

341
00:15:18,570 --> 00:15:19,850
Dezhi.

342
00:15:20,220 --> 00:15:21,700
My name is Yang Dezhi.

343
00:15:22,530 --> 00:15:23,279
What are these?

344
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,769
(Yang Dezhi, Officer of Division Four)

345
00:15:24,770 --> 00:15:26,859
(Officers of Division Four)
Daying, Zhigang, Yunkai,

346
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:27,809
Jingjing, and I

347
00:15:27,810 --> 00:15:29,771
put together a welcome gift.

348
00:15:29,772 --> 00:15:31,049
- Yes.
- Please accept the gift.

349
00:15:31,050 --> 00:15:33,420
If there's anything we've overlooked,
please forgive us.

350
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:36,259
We don't know

351
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:38,460
what you like yet.

352
00:15:38,930 --> 00:15:40,610
Just say the word.

353
00:15:40,770 --> 00:15:43,049
Do the other Division chiefs
have a lot of preferences?

354
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:43,899
They sure do.

355
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:44,912
The chief of Division One

356
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:47,119
loves sunflower seeds,
especially the ones from Xinjiang.

357
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,880
Slow-roasted
in an iron wok with coarse sand.

358
00:15:48,890 --> 00:15:50,630
Salty shells, mild kernels.
250 g every day.

359
00:15:50,672 --> 00:15:51,920
The chief of Division Two

360
00:15:51,930 --> 00:15:53,259
has two boiled eggs every morning.

361
00:15:53,260 --> 00:15:54,649
Boiled over low heat for 15 minutes,

362
00:15:54,650 --> 00:15:56,190
peeled, and then served on a jade dish.

363
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:58,310
In the afternoon, he drinks
premium Baihao Yinzhen tea.

364
00:15:58,310 --> 00:16:00,270
In the evening,
it's Lapsang Souchong black tea.

365
00:16:00,288 --> 00:16:01,250
It smooths the throat.

366
00:16:01,690 --> 00:16:02,660
Are you done?

367
00:16:03,380 --> 00:16:04,420
Yes.

368
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:05,940
May I ask,

369
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,649
what would you like?

370
00:16:07,650 --> 00:16:09,379
We're at your disposal.

371
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:10,649
- Yes.
- That's right.

372
00:16:10,650 --> 00:16:11,809
Just tell us.

373
00:16:11,810 --> 00:16:13,250
I only have one request.

374
00:16:14,410 --> 00:16:18,250
Take all this away. Now.

375
00:16:18,450 --> 00:16:19,850
And get back to work.

376
00:16:25,570 --> 00:16:26,700
Hold on.

377
00:16:28,650 --> 00:16:30,010
Where's the Archive Room?

378
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,120
(Jingshi Police Department, Archives)

379
00:16:49,690 --> 00:16:50,890
Cuban cigars.

380
00:16:50,980 --> 00:16:52,049
A special royal edition.

381
00:16:52,050 --> 00:16:53,529
Got them from the American Consul.

382
00:16:53,530 --> 00:16:54,970
Money can't buy these.

383
00:16:55,020 --> 00:16:55,689
Try them.

384
00:16:55,690 --> 00:16:57,800
(Chief Cao, Household Registry Division)
They're rare.

385
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:03,060
But no rare treasure is worth that much.

386
00:17:03,380 --> 00:17:04,730
I can't help you.

387
00:17:05,100 --> 00:17:06,299
No one is allowed to look into

388
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:08,050
the Gu Xishan case.

389
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:11,180
I'm not sticking my hand
into a hornet's nest.

390
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:12,700
Can't do it.

391
00:17:13,970 --> 00:17:14,940
Fair enough.

392
00:17:17,260 --> 00:17:19,449
I'll have a word with your wife
about your secret stash.

393
00:17:19,450 --> 00:17:20,409
Young Master!

394
00:17:20,410 --> 00:17:21,619
Young Master.

395
00:17:21,620 --> 00:17:22,460
Oh, please.

396
00:17:22,540 --> 00:17:24,660
Please don't do that.

397
00:17:24,820 --> 00:17:27,180
You'll get me into big trouble.

398
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:34,680
(Household Registry Division,
Jingshi Police Department)

399
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:48,080
(Jingshi Police Department
Household Records. Yuan Yuyin)

400
00:17:56,620 --> 00:17:57,620
It's you?

401
00:17:57,730 --> 00:17:58,970
Chief Yuan.

402
00:17:59,340 --> 00:18:00,570
Do you know him?

403
00:18:00,580 --> 00:18:01,420
No.

404
00:18:01,952 --> 00:18:03,090
You left me in danger earlier,

405
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:04,460
and now you say you don't know me?

406
00:18:08,450 --> 00:18:09,530
Chief Yuan.

407
00:18:10,210 --> 00:18:11,449
Chief Yuan,

408
00:18:11,450 --> 00:18:13,139
he's the son of Minister Zhao Chengru

409
00:18:13,140 --> 00:18:14,449
of Education.

410
00:18:14,450 --> 00:18:16,330
He's one of us.

411
00:18:21,136 --> 00:18:22,990
Since he's not
with the police department,

412
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,900
he's not allowed to enter
the archive room.

413
00:18:24,930 --> 00:18:26,570
You know the rules, Chief Cao.

414
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:28,139
Chief Yuan,

415
00:18:28,140 --> 00:18:29,072
he's one of us.

416
00:18:29,104 --> 00:18:31,290
We'll have
Young Master Zhao host a banquet

417
00:18:31,300 --> 00:18:32,491
at Tiansheng Restaurant,

418
00:18:32,492 --> 00:18:33,729
so you two can get acquainted.

419
00:18:33,730 --> 00:18:34,570
Sorry.

420
00:18:34,690 --> 00:18:35,860
I don't drink.

421
00:18:39,650 --> 00:18:40,449
Who is he?

422
00:18:40,450 --> 00:18:41,489
He's cocky.

423
00:18:41,490 --> 00:18:43,059
The Commissioner never mentioned it.

424
00:18:43,060 --> 00:18:44,624
All I know is
he came from the military.

425
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:46,220
He was sent from above.

426
00:18:47,170 --> 00:18:48,330
Chief,

427
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:49,419
this is bad.

428
00:18:49,420 --> 00:18:50,660
Something has happened!

429
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:54,880
(End of Episode 1)

430
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:57,800
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

431
00:18:57,800 --> 00:18:59,340
♪Troubled times
are but a laughing matter♪

432
00:18:59,340 --> 00:19:00,590
♪However, the world changes♪

433
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:02,510
♪You'll still be by my side♪

434
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:04,200
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

435
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:05,770
♪Praise and blame come and go♪

436
00:19:05,770 --> 00:19:07,340
♪If this is my final chapter♪

437
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:09,840
♪I'll solve this mystery with you♪
